# Keep image lean and avoid baking in host-user-owned artifacts
# that would cause permission errors at runtime.
#
# NOTE: dbt_project/target/ is INTENTIONALLY NOT ignored.
# CI runs `dagster-dbt project prepare-and-package` before docker build,
# which writes target/manifest.json. The Dagster user-deployment pod needs
# this manifest at image load time (@dbt_assets decorator).
dbt_project/logs/
dbt_project/dbt_packages/
dbt_project/.user.yml
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
